{"tid":1222568,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[DIY]如何和理非地衝擊警權合法性","createTime":"2019-06-14T12:58:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T14:01:40.000Z","uid":161626,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c5c10bf686e947991460e4a2aa81c6a3aff73d49","tid":1222568,"uid":161626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:58:41.000Z","msg":"網民已經好清楚黑警嘅暴行，但仍然有好多廢老啊叔師奶小朋友日日睇TVB<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔知道黑警喺612有幾失控<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府每年花咁多錢洗白警隊形象<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又喺學校教啲細路警察係善良正義嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就係為咗要維護警權、政權嘅合法性，令市民信任警察，同警方合作<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同埋吸引更多新血加入警隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地要做嘅嘢，就係去抗衡政府花大錢推廣嘅論述，破壞佢嘅合法性，加重佢嘅管治成本<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而今次黑警嘅失控表現，就係最好嘅材料：大家可以製作以下依啲展示板，喺遊行、地鐵（三個人以下啊）、機場、街市、學校門口、海外，俾各地市民親眼見到黑警嘅所作所為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />令全香港、全世界所有市民，尤其係下一代知道，香港警察只係港共殘暴政權嘅走狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oUQkssz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoUQkssz.jpg&h=a6b940a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n製作材料：大紙皮、彩印圖片、包書膠、膠紙、雙面膠紙。就係咁簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依條link有我準備好嘅A4比例圖片，直接印出來就用得。<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1k8HM6xhMSt-olDJsfaQ8r41S6XR-DgTp?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fdrive%2Ffolders%2F1k8HM6xhMSt-olDJsfaQ8r41S6XR-DgTp%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=Q%2BwKghBkVpQFldJLXg3PjXwORrEXjPgA%2FW0mwV49OOk%3D&h=57df5bca\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1k8HM6xhMSt-olDJsfaQ8r41S6XR-DgTp?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n你都可以搵啲更高清嘅相，去<a href=\"http://www.getpaint.net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.getpaint.net&d=Q%2BwKghBkVpQFldJLXg3PjXwORrEXjPgA%2FW0mwV49OOk%3D&h=0c632c8b\" target=\"_blank\">www.getpaint.net</a>下戴免費軟件，將圖片crop成 1:1.414 依個比例(A4)印出來。<br />\n<br />\n就算唔上前線，都有好多嘢值得做！"},{"pid":"a52c6f786f09f2366fdb34c5d8016fbf5b838290","tid":1222568,"uid":161626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:07:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"402f9d24c2f2787769399e10524eb238bcac3bfa","tid":1222568,"uid":176550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:09:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8c47e9c785fe9758d32e6cc24afa2831387904bc","tid":1222568,"uid":161626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:15:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7589eea10701e285392468284ccec6e66940150c","tid":1222568,"uid":161626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:31:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"244f861a00523f67f7d2f2f532af21c676e50dd2","tid":1222568,"uid":161626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T14:01:40.000Z","msg":"推"}]}